Global Climate App Privacy Policy
Effective date: September 06, 2019
This app does not collect any personal data.
No cookies
No personal data
No location information
No Google Analytics
No advertising
No IP addresses
The app downloads images over a secure internet connection to be displayed. Some images
are temporarily stored on the device. It saves settings on the device. If app is deleted no data
is left on the device.
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
By email:
By visiting this page on our website: https://i-logic.com/contact.htm
